ECE 422 Project 1
George Antonious (1396458)

Building:

To build on Linux do:
make linux

To build on OS X do:
make darwin

Running:

Before running make sure you include the current directory in you library path:
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:.

To generate the data do:
java GeneratorDriver <input_filename> <num_entries>

To attempt to sort the data do:
java SortDriver <input_filename> <output_filename> <primary_fail_rate> <backup_fail_rate> <timeout>